This is how to will_it_fly of q and w:
  Remember that total is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this q's length times:
    Increase total by item i in q
    Increase i
  End do
  When total is more than w, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  Remember that left is 0
  Remember that right is diff of q's length and 1
  Do this q's length times:
    When left is at least right, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When item left in q is not item right in q, then:
      The answer is 0
    End when
    Increase left
    Decrease right
  End do
  The answer is 1
